sion-text-1\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><p>FinRobo Advisor Securities Investment Consulting Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &#8220;the Company&#8221;) complies with the relevant laws and regulations, including the Personal Data Protection Act. In the course of operating within the approved business scope authorized by the competent authority, the Company may collect, process, or use your personal information for specific purposes. This data will only be processed or utilized before entering into financial product service contracts, during the contractual period, and within the retention period specified by law.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-2\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><p>Your personal information will primarily be stored in electronic or paper form within or outside the country&#8217;s territory and may be processed and utilized by the Company or its outsourced vendors (including international transmission). The scope of use includes providing your personal information to outsourced vendors or third parties with a cooperative or commissioned relationship with the Company, as well as to financial supervisory authorities, judicial authorities, or other entities specified by the competent authority, institutions, or individuals as required by relevant laws.<\/p>\n<p>The Company adheres to its Personal Data Management Policy and has established a Personal Data Protection Management System to guide the collection, processing, and use of any personal information. Therefore, you can comfortably provide your personal information to the Company.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-3\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><p>While retaining your personal information, in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act of our country, you have the following rights:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Inquire or request access to your personal information.<\/li>\n<li>Request a copy of your personal information.<\/li>\n<li>Request supplementation or correction of your personal information.<\/li>\n<li>Request the cessation of the collection, processing, or use of your personal information.<\/li>\n<li>Request the deletion of your personal information.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-4\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><p>When you wish to exercise the aforementioned rights, the Company and its branches can handle your requests. You can find our contact phone number and address on our official website.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-5\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><p>When the Company needs to collect, process, or use your personal information for the reasons mentioned above, you are free to choose whether to provide your personal information. If you choose not to provide personal information or provide incomplete information, the Company may not be able to provide you with complete services required for related business operations.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"100-width.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-4870","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.finroboadvisor.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4870"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.finroboadvisor.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.finroboadvisor.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.finroboadvisor.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.finroboadvisor.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4870"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/www.finroboadvisor.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4870\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4975,"href":"https:\/\/www.finroboadvisor.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4870